description.narrative: UNICEF Bangladesh delivered cross-sectoral services and opportunities in reinforcing governance and decentralization of operations and budget management with Divisional Implementation Plans developed and implemented by field offices. Regular PMT/OPMT monthly meetings where programme and operations performance at the technical level were discussed and corrective measures taken on underperforming areas greatly contributed to enhancing overall management of the office and programme delivery. UNICEF continued to play a leadership role in common approach with other UN agencies. UNICEF staff led four of the five OMT task forces established in 2019. All UN agencies continued to piggyback on LTAs established by UNICEF. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
